org.jpl7.fli

Class atom_t

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpl7.fli.LongHolder
      • org.jpl7.fli.atom_t

  • public class atom_t
extends LongHolder
    An atom_t is a specialised LongHolder which decrements its atom's reference count when garbage-collected (finalized).
